,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"第一次去都係去熱門旅遊景點啦<br />\n始終去到東京唔去鐵塔，迪士尼，秋葉原，築地，雷門，台場，涉谷，銀座，咁去來做乜？你都唔好意思同人講去過東京啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實東京係好大，當你去過2-3次，熟哂路之後，到時先去啲隱蔽地方都唔遲啦"},{"pid":"4b6a51c46f7857b3d0fb5955519c60c08f1772ea","tid":782530,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c5653d36627816dbadc5f51c48b4072445c64c7","tid":782530,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"debaae681c0af5785a68d21e7dcc91a6004ad645","tid":782530,"uid":98659,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T21:21:50.000Z","msg":"D伸手黨岩去青木原樹海<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死撚左佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T21:44:42.000Z","msg":"好像去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5毛發現"}]}